Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: travel advisor
des: Check before you go! Travel Advisor gives customers access to the 5 latest travel warnings issued by the U.S. government. Simply invoke the skill by saying "Alexa, open travel advisor" and then proceed by asking Alexa "are there any travel warnings I should be aware of?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
